{"tid":498957,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★手機上網變「龜速」，大鬧電訊公司涉襲警被捕","createTime":"2017-12-14T09:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T13:54:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a42babe39e6755b88d416c8870f5d40c6fac47e2","tid":498957,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T09:29:54.000Z","msg":"心急男擔心手機上網變「龜速」，大鬧電訊公司涉襲警被捕。現場為土瓜灣道247B號電訊數碼門市，昨(13日)晚8時許，一名任職裝修的姓黃(44歲)男子，到上址繳交96港元電話費，此時突然收到電訊公司短信，指其手機網絡首5GB數據快將用完，之後會按合約規定減慢上網速度，他閱畢即向職員投訴，更稱「唔公平，做咩要減我速」。職員向黃解釋此乃合約規定，並指下個月將會重新計算數據，惟黃不接受，更要求上級職員「同佢傾」，職員聯絡上級後，再繼續服務其他顧客。<br />\n<br />\n黃在等候期間懷疑遭冷待，突然情緒激動，在店內發難擲櫈，大吵大鬧。警員到場調解，惟有人未予理會，更出手襲擊警員，警員警告無效，遂用胡椒噴劑將黃制服。其後，4名警員合力將他抬上警車，期間黃仍極力掙扎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171214/bkn-20171214015343782-1214_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171214%2Fbkn-20171214015343782-1214_00822_001.html&d=VgOsMrzToc1whm0geNSfc4S5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=4a2a1b3c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171214/bkn-20171214015343782-1214_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d3c8c6d651c31d97b434660cec025763158b8353","tid":498957,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T09:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171214/photo/bkn-20171214015343782-1214_00822_001_02b.jpg?20171214165556\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171214015343782-1214_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20171214165556&h=af6bbffc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d67a3d41081019c02e79e8b3d2bf1e37e47a79c2","tid":498957,"uid":2654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T09:31:01.000Z","msg":"新世界移動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8342e8cff582085889db17ea8529417e47438d29","tid":498957,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T13: